          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How long does it take to get a new door installed in Annapolis, MD?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Most door replacements in Annapolis are completed in a single day. Capitol Improvements handles all measurements and fabrication in advance so installation day goes smoothly with minimal disruption to your household."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Do I need a permit to replace a door in Annapolis, MD?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Most residential door replacement projects in Annapolis do not require a building permit. However, homes within the Annapolis Historic District may be subject to additional local review requirements. Capitol Improvements always checks local requirements on your behalf to ensure your door project is fully compliant."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What type of door material is best for homes near the Chesapeake Bay in Annapolis?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Fiberglass and marine-grade wood doors are the top choices for Annapolis homes because they resist salt air corrosion, high humidity, and seasonal temperature swings far better than standard steel. Our team helps you choose the right material based on your home's exposure and style preferences."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can a new door be matched to existing colonial or craftsman trim in Annapolis?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Absolutely. Capitol Improvements carpenters carry custom knife profiles and can mill new casings on-site so your replacement door blends seamlessly with original colonial, craftsman, or mid-century moldings found throughout Annapolis neighborhoods. This ensures a finished look that respects your home's architectural character."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How much does door replacement cost in Annapolis, MD?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "The cost of door replacement in Annapolis varies based on door size, material, glass inserts, and hardware selections. Contact Capitol Improvements for a free estimate tailored to your specific project and Annapolis home."
          }
        },
        {
