            "text": "Yes. Capitol Improvements routinely handles door replacements on waterfront properties in Annapolis, including elevated deck entries, bulkhead access points, and outswing configurations required by local building codes. Every installation is designed to be watertight and storm-rated for lasting coastal performance."
